There is no information for this species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FC8E653B8755B10F1E385DC8F963F3D9" pageId="26" pageNumber="219" type="activity">
<paragraph id="B42B36B08755B10F1E385DC8F963F3D9" blockId="26.[1373,2583,1538,3305]" pageId="26" pageNumber="219">
<emphasis id="86E0EAA28755B10F1E385DC8F9DFF406" bold="true" box="[1377,1611,3034,3067]" pageId="26" pageNumber="219">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Narrow-skulled Pocket Mouse is nocturnal and terrestrial, and it is active throughout the year.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FC8E653B8755B10F1E3B5A3BF9A3F38E" pageId="26" pageNumber="219" type="biology_ecology">
